===[[Noun]]===
#A [[movement]] (usually involuntary) of the muscles of the face, particularly of the lips, with a peculiar [[expression]] of the eyes, indicating merriment, satisfaction, or derision, and usually attended by a sonorous and interrupted expulsion of air from the lungs. See [[laugh]], (intransitive verb)
#:'''Quotations'''
#:*The act of '''laughter''', which is a sweet contraction of the muscles of the face, and a pleasant agitation of the vocal organs, is not merely, or totally within the jurisdiction of ourselves. - [[Sir T. Browne]]
#:*Archly the maiden smiled, and with eyes overrunning with '''laughter''' - [[Longfellow]]
# The sound produced by air so expelled.

